graph LR
    TrainingOp[Training Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    TrainingOp -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+<br/>REQUIRED]
    TrainingOp -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.14.0+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling<br/>DEFAULT| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins v0.25.7+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|gang scheduling<br/>ALTERNATIVE| Volcano[Volcano<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>OPTIONAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|service mesh| Istio[Istio<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|UI integration| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL]
    TrainingOp -->|metrics scraping| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>INTERNAL]
    TrainingOp -.->|pod-to-pod mTLS| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>INTERNAL OPTIONAL]

    %% External Services
    TrainingOp -->|API access| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    TrainingOp -->|image pull| Registry[Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Registry -->|operator image| TrainingOp
    Registry -->|training images| TrainingPods[Training Worker Pods]

    %% CRD Dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|manages| PyTorchJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>PyTorchJob]
    TrainingOp -->|manages| TFJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>TFJob]
    TrainingOp -->|manages| MPIJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>MPIJob]
    TrainingOp -->|manages| XGBoostJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>XGBoostJob]
    TrainingOp -->|manages| MXJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>MXJob]
    TrainingOp -->|manages| PaddleJobCRD[kubeflow.org/v1<br/>PaddleJob]
    TrainingOp -->|gang scheduling| PodGroupCRD[PodGroup<br/>scheduling.x-k8s.io<br/>scheduling.volcano.sh]

    %% Pod creation
    PyTorchJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods
    TFJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods
    MPIJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods
    XGBoostJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods
    MXJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods
    PaddleJobCRD -->|creates| TrainingPods

    %% SDK Integration
    SDK[Python SDK<br/>TrainingClient] -->|submits| PyTorchJobCRD
    SDK -->|submits| TFJobCRD
    SDK -->|submits| MPIJobCRD
    User[Data Scientist] -->|uses| SDK

    %% Styling
    style TrainingOp fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style K8s fill:#0066cc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SchedulerPlugins fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Volcano fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style PrometheusOp fill:#9673a6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#0066cc,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Registry fill:#d6b656,stroke:#333
    style PyTorchJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style TFJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style MPIJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style XGBoostJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style MXJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style PaddleJobCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style PodGroupCRD fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style TrainingPods fill:#82b366,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SDK fill:#50e3c2,stroke:#333
    style User fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#999

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend
        L1[Solid line: Required dependency]
        L2[Dashed line: Optional dependency]
    end

    style Legend fill:#fff,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style L1 fill:#fff,stroke:#333
    style L2 fill:#fff,stroke:#333
